{"type":"text","timestamp":1782577664667,"sessionID":"ses_0f618a962ffe1ahVHOzThVCMCm","part":{"id":"prt_f09e86db9001UL7GZ6aYNuCgp5","messageID":"msg_f09e862a7001xNaudlJkn7Pnno","sessionID":"ses_0f618a962ffe1ahVHOzThVCMCm","type":"text","text":"I’ve confirmed phase-03 build evidence exists and the phase test file already covers the intended pure logic. I’m now patching the matrix rows so the login/onboarding cluster closes on precise functions plus explicit `harness-blocked` verification, instead of broad file/shell references.","time":{"start":1782577655225,"end":1782577664665}}}
